            p.wcu-card-description
              | Experience fine dining at the comfort of your home. All our orders are carefully packed and arranged to give you nothing less than perfect.
        .col-12.col-md-4
          .wcu-card.p-3.mb-3
            img.wcu-card-image(src="https://d1tgh8fmlzexmh.cloudfront.net/ccbp-responsive-website/fruits-img.png")
            h1.wcu-card-title.mt-3 Fresh Food
            p.wcu-card-description
              | The Fresh Food group provides fresh-cut fruits and vegetables directly picked from our partner farms and farm houses so that you always get them tree to plate.
        .col-12.col-md-4
          .wcu-card.p-3.mb-3
            img.wcu-card-image(src="https://d1tgh8fmlzexmh.cloudfront.net/ccbp-responsive-website/offers-img.png")
            h1.wcu-card-title.mt-3 Best Offers
            p.wcu-card-description
              | Food Coupons & Offers upto
